e xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 30, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104goa1709705635907.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/goa1709705635907.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/goa1709705635907.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"goa1709705635907\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This section provides description for the logical UX widget <code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-Switch</code>\n\t\tproperties.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"goa1709705635907__section_w1648ab1b5b1_w1649ab1b5_w1650ab1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"goa1709705635907__fig_dvm_frk_dhc\">\n<p class=\"p\">ux-Switch widget</p>\n<img alt=\"ux-Switch widget preview\" class=\"image\" id=\"goa1709705635907__image_e5z_hrk_dhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ux-Switch.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Summary</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__1\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__1\">Logical widget name:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-Switch</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__1\">Maps to physical widget:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"></code> of type boolean</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__1\">Default definition:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-Switch=uxSwitch()</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__1\">Supported triggers:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">onchange</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__1\">Use for:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"goa1709705635907__table_jjs_tks_q1c__entry__2\">Toggle button to display Boolean state</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kin1709198869557.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uxswitch</a><p>The uxswitch widget is a toggle field control. It always contains a field value, even if it is not a valid Boolean. Unlike the checkbox widget, the uxswitch widget does not provide the indeterminate state, so null value or empty (\"\") value results in a format error.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lzi1701171069984.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UX Widgets</a><p>Uniface UX provides a set of widgets that are implemented using the UX Widget Interface. This set is referred as UX Widgets. The sources of these widgets are available and allow changes and/or extensions to the widgets. In a default Uniface installation, you can find the sources in the &lt;install&gt;\\uniface\\webapps\\uniface\\common\\ux folder.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6398183\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6398183\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ux-Switch Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 30, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-Switch properties. ux-Switch widget Table 1. Widget Summary Property Description Logical widget name: ux-Switch Maps to physical widget: of type boolean Default definition: ux-Switch=uxSwitch() Supported triggers: onchange Use for: Toggle button to display Boolean state Related Links uxswitch The uxswitch widget is a toggle field control. It always contains a field value, even if it is not a valid Boolean. Unlike the checkbox widget, the uxswitch widget does not provide the indeterminate state, so null value or empty (\"\") value results in a format error. UX Widgets Uniface UX provides a set of widgets that are implemented using the UX Widget Interface. This set is referred as UX Widgets. The sources of these widgets are available and allow changes and/or extensions to the widgets. In a default Uniface installation, you can find the sources in the <install>\\uniface\\webapps\\uniface\\common\\ux folder. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}